{"tid":1961193,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"大公文匯傳媒集團譴責狂徒寄出含「不明粉末」信件","createTime":"2020-04-06T15:21:48.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-07T04:09:36.000Z","uid":212626,"like":35,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":42,"replies":[{"pid":"b019fe010faee65b8a1360166978457621a90157","tid":1961193,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-06T15:21:48.000Z","msg":"灣仔軒尼詩道與柯布連道交界的萬寶樓，一個單位下午四時許收到一封信，職員打開時發現內藏白色粉末，懷疑是危險化學品報警。警方爆炸品處理課人員到場，封鎖現場調查，初步相信白色粉末是<span style=\"color: red;\">麵粉</span>，案件交由灣仔警區重案組跟進。現場消息指，有關單位是文匯報的物業，目前開設一間中資小型公司。<br />\n<br />\n大公文匯傳媒集團發聲明，強烈譴責有狂徒向文匯報寄出含不明粉末及恐嚇字句的信件，<span style=\"color: red;\">指恐嚇行為是對香港法治及新聞自由的公然挑戰，集團絕不會向泛暴派和黑惡勢力低頭</span>，相信警方會深入調查，盡快將違法暴力者繩之於法。<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1279116&amp;csid=261_341\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2FPage%2FZH-TW%2Fnewsdetail.aspx%3FItemId%3D1279116%26csid%3D261_341&d=oVNa%2F3rGcR5VJv77DJ2lexckzRVyZutP2gug%2B5Lqx%2Fc%3D&h=80159901\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1279116&amp;csid=261_341</a><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eca653eb110459f8a93f7db95017f76865cfa05a","tid":1961193,"uid":187957,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-06T15:22:20.000Z","msg":"呢排拍戲班人冇野撈<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3e9d4ebbe3a22313c790694c0718b6562da33e34","tid":1961193,"uid":8745,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-06T15:22:38.000Z","msg":"好心寄消毒粉俾你地仲嫌棄"},{"pid":"fc2d34768bcbed7fa5952e4a888af18af8e9e196","tid":1961193,"uid":252142,"like":26,"dislike":0,"score":26,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-04-06T15:24:49.000Z","msg":"寄麵粉=狂徒？<br />\n咁我樓下既麵包鋪師傅=恐怖分子？"},{"pid":"8367b958dc8be2c418c34b41d5bdb3047c2ffca1","tid":1961193,"uid":212626,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-06T15:24:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/